HEADWORD: malheur wire lettuce
<hw>malheur wire lettuce</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
small mustardlike plant (<spn>Stephanomeria malheurensis</spn>) of
Oregon, belonging to the family <fam>Cruciferae</fam>; it is a
threatened species.</def>⟦br⟧
